{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.reduction_sys\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">reduction_sys</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This attribute calls the `reduction_notation` command for the annotated declaration, such as in:\n\n```\n@[reduction rs \"ₙ\", simp]\ndef PredReduction (a b : ℕ) : Prop := a = b + 1\n```\n","docLink":"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.reduction_sys","kind":"def","line":115,"name":"Cslib.reduction_sys","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/7f88669e78c0fa9d9c4f41a397072114cbb9aa7e/Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.lean#L115-L123"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.command_Reduction_notation__\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">command_Reduction_notation__</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"This command adds notations for a `ReductionSystem.Red` and `ReductionSystem.MRed`. This should\nnot usually be called directly, but from the `reduction_sys` attribute.\n\nAs an example `reduction_notation foo \"β\"` will add the notations \"⭢β\" and \"↠β\".\n\nNote that the string used will afterwards be registered as a notation. This means that if you have\nalso used this as a constructor name, you will need quotes to access corresponding cases, e.g. «β»\nin the above example.\n","docLink":"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.command_Reduction_notation__","kind":"def","line":87,"name":"Cslib.command_Reduction_notation__","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/7f88669e78c0fa9d9c4f41a397072114cbb9aa7e/Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.lean#L87-L97"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.commandCreate_reduction_sys__\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">commandCreate_reduction_sys__</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.ParserDescr\">Lean.ParserDescr</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A command to create a `ReductionSystem` from a relation, robust to use of `variable `","docLink":"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.commandCreate_reduction_sys__","kind":"def","line":58,"name":"Cslib.commandCreate_reduction_sys__","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/7f88669e78c0fa9d9c4f41a397072114cbb9aa7e/Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.lean#L58-L85"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Foundations/Semantics/ReductionSystem/Basic.html#Cslib.ReductionSystem.MRed.single\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">ReductionSystem</span>.<span class=\"name\">MRed</span>.<span class=\"name\">single</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">Term</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">a </span><span class=\"fn\">b</span> : <span class=\"fn\">Term</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span cl